---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - Gas Town Hall"
  description="Privacy policy for Gas Town Hall. We respect your privacy and collect minimal data."
>
  <div class="privacy-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        Gas Town Hall is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy
        explains what information we collect and how we use it.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use <a href="https://plausible.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          >Plausible Analytics</a
        >, a privacy-friendly analytics service that:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Does not use cookies</li>
        <li>Does not collect personal data</li>
        <li>Does not track you across websites</li>
        <li>Is fully compliant with GDPR, CCPA, and PECR</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Plausible collects only aggregate, anonymized data such as page views,
        referrer sources, and general geographic regions. No individual user can
        be identified.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you visit Gas Town Hall, we collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Page views:</strong> Which pages are visited (anonymized, aggregated)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Referrer:</strong> Where visitors come from (search engines, social
          media, etc.)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Device type:</strong> Desktop, mobile, or tablet (no fingerprinting)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Country:</strong> General geographic region (not precise location)
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data We Don't Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Personal information (names, emails, addresses)</li>
        <li>IP addresses (not stored or logged)</li>
        <li>Cookies or tracking identifiers</li>
        <li>Cross-site browsing history</li>
        <li>Device fingerprints</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Our documentation may contain links to external services like GitHub,
        Discord, and X (Twitter). These services have their own privacy policies
        that apply when you visit them.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, you can reach us at <a
          href="mailto:gastownhall@gmail.com">gastownhall@gmail.com</a
        >, on <a
          href="https://discord.gg/xHpUGUzZp2"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">Discord</a
        >, or on <a
          href="https://x.com/gastownhall"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">X</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #666);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-primary, #e94560);
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
